"author_location":"Delhi, India"}},"review_fGFNWC":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_1_2026_01_39_49_PM.png","star_rating":5,"review_text":"Finally, shorts that actually fit perfectly and support high-impact cardio. The lycra fabric is so soft yet durable. Worth every rupee.","author_name":"Priya M.","author_location":"Mumbai, India"}},"review_yz4XEb":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_3be7e8fd-34b9-4355-bbec-105ef47b68e7.jpg","star_rating":5,"review_text":"I wore the Air Flex track pants for my morning run and had zero discomfort. Absolutely premium quality gear for this price.","author_name":"Arjun T.","author_location":"Bangalore, India"}},"review_mQabat":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_e8604dc8-aa30-4634-8ed0-704e6b7d6b76.jpg","star_rating":5,"review_text":"The aesthetics are on point. I wear the joggers to the gym and out for chai. Fits perfectly and looks great.","author_name":"Sneha D.","author_location":"Pune, India"}},"review_Cg4UEG":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitleddesign_50.jpg","star_rating":5,"review_text":"Fast delivery and the packaging was premium. You can tell 11FIT cares about every detail. Ordered again within a week.","author_name":"Vikram K.","author_location":"Hyderabad, India"}}},"block_order":["review_QERBAr","review_fGFNWC","review_yz4XEb","review_mQabat","review_Cg4UEG"],"name":"11FIT Club Reviews","settings":{"section_title":"Club Reviews","section_subtitle":"Athletes Trust 11FIT","bg_color":"#ffffff","title_color":"#c5a059","auto_scroll_delay":"3500"}},"11fit_support_faq_BAdFVN":{"type":"11fit-support-faq","blocks":{"faq_item_cACHir":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"What fabric is used in 11FIT products?","answer":"All our products use premium imported fabrics including Four-Way Lycra (250+ GSM), NS Terry Lycra, and Air-Lite NS — highly stretchable, breathable, and built for performance."}},"faq_item_Dpd77t":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"What fabric is used in 11FIT products?","answer":"We use premium quality sportswear fabrics. Our activewear features Imported Four-Way Lycra, which is highly stretchable, breathable, and has a heavy 250+ GSM for a rich feel. For casual wear we offer lightweight NS (Non-Stretchable) fabrics, as well as premium NS Terry Lycra and Air-Lite NS fabrics."}},"faq_item_97FP4R":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"How do I find my correct size?","answer":"We offer sizes from M to XXL. For track pants: Medium fits a 28–30 inch waist, Large fits 30–32 inches, XL fits 32–34 inches, and XXL fits 34–36 inches. Detailed size charts are available on every product page."}},"faq_item_RKrK8a":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Which courier services do you use?","answer":"We provide doorstep delivery across India using trusted courier partners including Blue Dart, DTDC, Delhivery, and Xpressbees — ensuring your gear arrives quickly and safely."}},"faq_item_KqR6Bn":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"What is your return and refund policy?","answer":"We want you to train in gear you love! If there is a sizing issue or you are not completely satisfied, we offer a hassle-free return and refund within 7 days of receiving your order. Just contact our support team."}},"faq_item_gpprcn":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"What payment methods do you accept?","answer":"We offer a variety of secure payment options. You can pay via Cash on Delivery (COD), or use prepaid options including UPI, GPay, Paytm, PhonePe, and Credit\/Debit Cards."}},"faq_item_EqCqhz":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Is free shipping available?","answer":"Yes! We offer free shipping on all orders above ₹499. Orders below this amount will have a nominal delivery charge applied at checkout."}}},"block_order":["faq_item_cACHir","faq_item_Dpd77t","faq_item_97FP4R","faq_item_RKrK8a","faq_item_KqR6Bn","faq_item_gpprcn","faq_item_EqCqhz"],"name":"11FIT Support & FAQ","settings":{"section_title":"Support & FAQ","section_subtitle":"Everything You Need To Know","bg_color":"#f4f4f4","title_color":"#c5a059","question_font":"Poppins","question_font_size":13,"answer_font":"Poppins","answer_font_size":12,"faq_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_1_2026_05_12_52_PM.png","image_brightness":65,"overlay_heading":"Premium","overlay_subtext":"Engineered For Athletes"}}},"order":["image_banner","ullukart_hero_LwyDx3","ullukart_marquee1_GXAPyT","ullukart_category_bubbles_wmm7Lw","ullukart_3d_deal_LLyATX","ullukart_2x2_grid_F4nxF3","ullukart_flash_sale_L4kxCW","ullukart_dual_promos_67YCGA","ullukart_tabbed_slider_wJVpcN","1779990702925557f3","11fit_club_reviews_dzNCHU","11fit_support_faq_BAdFVN"]}